Racial Traits ~ Tortle	CATEGORY:Internal	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Tortle Selection|1|TYPE=BASE

###Block: Tortle
Size					KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Size				SORTKEY:1_Race1	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You are Medium or Small. You choose the size when you select this race.
Creature Type			KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Creature Type		SORTKEY:1_Race2	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You are a Humanoid.
#Claws					KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Claws				SORTKEY:1_Race3	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You have claws that you can use to make unarmed strikes. When you hit with them, the strike deals 1d6 + your Strength modifier slashing damage, instead of the bludgeoning damage normal for an unarmed strike.																																																																																																																																																												BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base																					SOURCEPAGE:p.119
Speed					KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Speed				SORTKEY:1_Race4	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your walking speed is 30 feet.
Hold Breath				KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Hold Breath			SORTKEY:1_Race5	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You can hold your breath for up to 1 hour.
#Natural Armor			KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Natural Armor		SORTKEY:1_Race6	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your shell provides you a base AC of 17 (your Dexterity modifier doesn’t affect this number). You can’t wear light, medium, or heavy armor, but if you are using a shield, you can apply the shield’s bonus as normal.
#Nature's Intuition		KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Nature's Intuition	SORTKEY:1_Race6	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Thanks to your mystical connection to nature, you gain proficiency with one of the following skills of your choice: Animal Handling, Medicine, Nature, Perception, Stealth, or Survival.
#Shell Defense			KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Shell Defense		SORTKEY:1_Race6	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You can withdraw into your shell as an action. Until you emerge, you gain a +4 bonus to your AC, and you have advantage on Strength and Constitution saving throws. While in your shell, you are prone, your speed is 0 and can’t increase, you have disadvantage on Dexterity saving throws, you can’t take reactions, and the only action you can take is a bonus action to emerge from your shell.
#Languages				KEY:MPMotM Tortle ~ Languages			SORTKEY:1_Race6	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Tortle Race Trait.MPMotM Tortle Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your character can speak, read, and write Common and one other language that you and your DM agree is appropriate for the character. The Player’s Handbook offers a list of languages to choose from. The DM is free to modify that list for a campaign.
